        public void startJob(Policy policy,
                     java.util.Date effDate,
                     CalculationMethod refundCalcMethod)
              throws com.guidewire.pl.web.controller.UserDisplayableException
        Starts a cancellation job on the latest bound period of the passed-in policy that includes the given effective date.
        Parameters:
        policy - The policy for which the job is to be started
        effDate - The date at which the job should be started.
        refundCalcMethod - the calculation method used to figure the refund
        Throws:

        Same as startJob() but commits the job's bundle after starting the job.
        Parameters:
        policy - The policy for which the job is to be started
